headline: Cadence Design Systems, Inc. (CDNS): A Bull Case Theory
summary: We came across a bullish thesis on Cadence Design Systems, Inc. (CDNS) on Compound & Fire’s Substack. In this article, we will summarize the bulls’ thesis on CDNS. Cadence Design Systems, Inc. (CDNS)’s share was trading at $ 307.2 as of 11th June. CDNS’s trailing and forward P/E were 76.56 and 44.44 respectively according to Yahoo Finance. […]
